This file describes the communication protocol between the client and the server. It consists of a command followed by parameters. The string must end with a \n.

=== Protocol ===

SET
	OID=[filterchain/filterchain:filter/input]
	PID=[property/"position"/"active"]
	VALUE=[int/float/boolean]
	
INFO
	OID=[filterchain/filterchain:filter/input/"all"]
	PID=[property/"active"/"all"]
	
CREATE
	OBJECT=["input"/"filter"/"filterchain"]
	TYPE=[input_type/filter_type/]   Note:This field is optional
	ID=[id]

SAVE
	OID=["input"/"filterchain"]
	
=== Examples ===

Create a filterchain and a filter
	CREATE TYPE=filterchain ID=my_filterchain
	CREATE TYPE=filter TYPE=GRAYSCALE2RGB ID=my_g2r
	
Add the filter
	SET OID=my_filterchain:my_g2r PID=active VALUE=true

Activate a source (defined in config file)
	SET OID=my_camera PID=active VALUE=true
	
Activate the filterchain
	SET OID=my_filterchain PID=active VALUE=true


